<HEADLINE>
<P>
TO OUR READERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Wine comments have now been incorporated into the restaurant review. We've 
also changed some of the information at the end of the review.Unless otherwise 
noted, we assume that restaurants accept major credit cards and offer valet 
parking and a full bar. Since most restaurants are open daily for lunch and 
dinner, we will list only the exceptions. 
</P>
