 * * * Ronnie Cuber, "The Scene Is Clean," Milestone. Best known as a muscular 
baritone sax soloist, Cuber extends himself here playing tenor and alto saxes, 
flute and composing/arranging most of the charts, which have a generally Latin 
tinge -- even on "Flamingo."Geoff Keezer's piano and, on two cuts, Joey De 
Francesco's organ, embellish the jubilant ambience, highlighted by "Adoracion" 
and "Arroz Con Pollo." 
</P>
