along with new Capitol President Gary Gersh, Robertson is putting the finishing 
touches on his first album for the label -- a soundtrack for the documentary 
series "The Native Americans," featuring a collection of native performers from 
across North America. Robertson is also co-writing songs with Eric Clapton for 
a 1995 album by the English guitarist that Robertson will produce. Steve 
Hochman 
