California: 4,000 Florida: 2,500 New York: 2,200 Pennsylvania: 1,800 Texas: 
1,600 Illinois: 1,300 Ohio: 1,300 New Jersey: 1,100 North Carolina: 1,000 
Massachusetts: 950 Source: American Cancer Society  
