31 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
SINGER ESTEFAN EXPECTING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Singer Gloria Estefan, who passed up a concert tour, film roles and other 
engagements to try to get pregnant, is expecting her second child on Dec. 4, 
the Miami Herald reported Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
