</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Pacific Asian Consortium in Employment is offering free loan packaging for 
business owners affected by the Jan. 17 earthquake. 
</P>
<P>
 PACE staff members fluent in Spanish, Korean or English will assist qualified 
business owners in packaging their disaster loans, which may include compiling 
or reconstructing financial statements and projections required by the Small 
Business Administration. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: Isabel Duran or Lauren Park, (213) 382-2936. 
