COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTH: SOUTH-CENTRAL; MEETING TO FOCUS ON REVITALIZATION PLANS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Residents, merchants and property owners are invited to attend a meeting on 
June 28 of the Council 9 Community Advisory Committee to discuss revitalization 
plans. 
</P>
<P>
 The meeting, at 5200 S. Central Ave., will begin at 5:45 p.m. Two discussion 
