BRIEFLY; SCHOLARSHIP: VENICE HIGH FRESHMAN AWARDED $12,000 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A Venice High School freshman has won a $12,000 college scholarship, one of 
five such scholarships awarded to Los Angeles Unified School District students. 
</P>
<P>
 Le My Hoang was a recipient of the Warren Christopher Scholarship, established 
for Los Angeles Unified School district students. 
</P>
<P>
