a Los Angeles law firm headed by Christopher until he was appointed secretary 
of state. Christopher is an alumnus of Hollywood High School. 
</P>
<P>
 For each of Hoang's three remaining years of high school, $4,000 will be set 
aside for her college education. If Hoang maintains a cumulative 3.25 
grade-point average, she will receive an additional $4,000 for college. 
</P>
