WOMEN IN ARCHITECTURE HONOR THREE UCLA GRADUATE STUDENTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rebecca Fenno has been named as the recipient of the top scholarship prize of 
$2,500 by the Assn. for Women in Architecture (AWA), with Patricia Solis, 
second-place winner, and Susan Hickey, in third place.All are UCLA graduate 
students. 
</P>
