between Ventura Avenue and Fir Street. The Children's Push 'em-Pull 'em Parade 
is 10:30 a.m. Free. (805) 654-7830. An evening celebration awaits on the 
athletic field at Ventura College, 4667 Telegraph Road. Gates open at 5:30 
p.m.; entertainment and games are at 6, and fireworks are at 8:55. $8, general; 
$6, kids. (805) 654-6462. 
