Tour, July 23. Twenty-, 40- and 62.1-mile scenic rides are through the 
Alexander, Russian River and Dry Creek valleys. $22 before July 4; $32 after. 
Space is limited; no same-day registration. (707) 433-6935. MARY FRANCES SMITH 
