NEWS, TIPS & BARGAINS; CARIBBEAN WEDDING, NO WAITING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Want to get hitched in a hurry? Barbados has done away with its six-day 
waiting period and now allows couples to arrive on the Caribbean island, apply 
for a license and get married all on the same day. 
</P>
</TEXT>
